<para style="p">For the chief musician; after the manner of Jeduthun. A psalm of David.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />I wait in silence for God alone;</para>

<para style="q1">my salvation comes from him.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />He alone is my rock and my salvation;</para>

<para style="q1">he is my high tower; I will not be greatly moved.</para>
